{"tid":1091354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁愛詩：社會對修訂逃犯條例的憂慮是多餘","createTime":"2019-04-04T05:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T16:11:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"52a59c1fc4454353f56e0bc37ea7382a6436a2ce","tid":1091354,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:25:34.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】基本法委員會前副主任梁愛詩認為，之前未有與中國訂立長期移交逃犯協議，只是因為回歸初期港人對一國兩制信心不足，現時內地司法制度已有進步，社會對修訂逃犯條例的憂慮只是多餘。<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會前副主任梁愛詩：「經過二十年了，二十年這麼長時間，中國亦經歷了司法改革，是否說一些進步也沒有？而且如果說某個國家司法水平，香港與那麼多個國家有簽訂(長期移交協議)，是否每個國家司法水平也一樣，或比我們更好？」"},{"pid":"c167c3a48ca18f8e00d4587e89e33cd8ef792cc4","tid":1091354,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=343316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D343316&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=4867ca8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D343316&h=b7fb174f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=343316</a>"},{"pid":"a71476add0216dfabd9d88c041d7cfd0b0ca6665","tid":1091354,"uid":14918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:27:19.000Z","msg":"唔係社會<br />\n<br />\n係商界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8694d3db6b09cb2c5a4d5778f43841c140abe9","tid":1091354,"uid":70786,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:28:58.000Z","msg":"你條妖婦仲存在就係多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同香港有協議嘅國家司法起碼係合格水平<br />\n依家係冇人信支那法治呀"},{"pid":"15397c937255ff69d240ebeb0bcff940de6b50c3","tid":1091354,"uid":44562,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"梁愛詩對社會是多餘"},{"pid":"5f71a88a69d672f4236